[Quotes]
victory0 = "You're so useless not even Hell would want you, at least down there they look for entertainment."
victory1 = "I broke you like a cheap toy... though even a toy lasts longer than you, piece of trash."
victory2 = "Your ki was so weak Dr. Gero would’ve killed himself before using it as energy."
victory3 = "You died so fast even Shenron won’t remember your name, insect."
victory4 = "You screamed like a pig at slaughter... at least pigs feed someone, you’re not even good for that."
victory5 = "Hmph... I destroyed you so easily I almost feel guilty… like kicking a cripple."
victory6 = "Not even Frieza would waste his time torturing a pathetic wretch like you."
victory7 = "You’re so miserable that if they bring you back, the only thing you’ll achieve is dying again, more humiliated."
victory8 = "You know what you are? A bad joke even Mr. Satan would refuse to tell on stage."
victory9 = "I turned you to dust and you still smell worse than a dinosaur’s shit."


